      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Meticulously maintained and demonstrating robust mechanical integrity, this model offers a seamless blend of performance and daily reliability. The exterior retains its professional luster, while the interior remains refined and well-appointed. A superlative choice for those seeking proven quality and exceptional value.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
